    "# Notebook 09 \u2014 Assemblage final\n",
    "\n",
    "**Projet Drone Rescue \u2014 s\u00e9rie p\u00e9dagogique Python**\n",
    "\n",
    "Ce notebook r\u00e9unit TOUS les concepts vus dans nb\_01 \u00e0 nb\_08 :\n",
    "dictionnaires, grille, distance de Chebyshev, logique de jeu, console, log.\n",
    "\n",
    "> **Objectif** : \u00e9crire, de z\u00e9ro, un sc\u00e9nario de jeu complet en utilisant uniquement des fonctions pures (aucune POO)."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-concepts",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Concepts assembl\u00e9s\n",
    "\n",
    "| Concept | Vu dans |\n",
    "|---------|---------|\n",
    "| Dictionnaires imbriques | nb\_01, nb\_02 |\n",
    "| Grille 0-based + `pos_str` | nb\_03, nb\_04 |\n",
    "| Distance de Chebyshev | nb\_03 |\n",
    "| Dictionnaires avanc\u00e9s (`any`, `all`, comprehensions) | nb\_05 |\n",
    "| Affichage grille + ANSI | nb\_06 |\n",
    "| R\u00e8gles officielles (mouvement, co\u00fbt, batterie) | nb\_07 |\n",
    "| Log + historique | nb\_08 |\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-imports",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Imports et constantes\n",
    "\n",
    "On travaille en **mode autonome** : aucun import de `jeu/`. Tout est red\u00e9fini ici pour que le notebook soit autoportant."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "id": "cell-code-imports",
   "metadata": {},
   "execution_count": null,
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import random\n",
    "\n",
    "# --- Constantes du jeu ---\n",
    "TAILLE = 8          # grille 8x8\n",
    "LETTRES = 'ABCDEFGHIJ'[:TAILLE]\n",
    "BATTERIE_MAX = 20\n",
    "BATTERIE_INIT = 15\n",
    "RECHARGE_HOPITAL = 10\n",
    "COUT_TRANSPORT = 2   # co\u00fbt si survivant \u00e0 bord\n",
    "COUT_ZONE_X = 1      # co\u00fbt suppl\u00e9mentaire zone dangereuse\n",
    "NB_TOURS_MAX = 30\n",
    "PROBA_PROPAGATION = 0.4\n",
    "PROPAGATION_FREQUENCE = 5  # tous les 5 tours\n",
    "\n",
    "print('Constantes OK')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-fonctions-base",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. Fonctions utilitaires (rappel nb\_01 \u00e0 nb\_04)\n",
    "\n",
    "Repr\u00e9sentation des positions, distance de Chebyshev."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "id": "cell-code-utils",
   "metadata": {},
   "execution_count": null,
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def pos_str(col, lig):\n",
    "    \"\"\"Convertit (col, lig) 0-based en chaine lisible ex: B3.\"\"\"\n",
    "    return f\"{LETTRES[col]}{lig + 1}\"\n",
    "\n",
    "def distance_chebyshev(c1, l1, c2, l2):\n",
    "    \"\"\"Distance de Chebyshev entre deux cases (mouvement de roi aux \u00e9checs).\"\"\"\n",
    "    return max(abs(c2 - c1), abs(l2 - l1))\n",
    "\n",
    "def case_valide(col, lig):\n",
    "    return 0 <= col < TAILLE and 0 <= lig < TAILLE\n",
    "\n",
    "# Tests rapides\n",
    "assert pos_str(0, 0) == 'A1'\n",
    "assert pos_str(1, 2) == 'B3'\n",
    "assert distance_chebyshev(0, 0, 2, 1) == 2\n",
    "assert distance_chebyshev(3, 3, 4, 4) == 1\n",
    "print('Utilitaires OK')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-entites",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. Cr\u00e9ation des entit\u00e9s (rappel nb\_01, nb\_02)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "id": "cell-code-entites",
   "metadata": {},
   "execution_count": null,
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def creer_drone(did, col, lig):\n",
    "    return {\n",
    "        'id': did, 'col': col, 'lig': lig,\n",
    "        'batterie': BATTERIE_INIT, 'batterie_max': BATTERIE_MAX,\n",
    "        'survivant': None, 'bloque': 0, 'hors_service': False\n",
    "    }\n",
    "\n",
    "def creer_survivant(sid, col, lig):\n",
    "    return {'id': sid, 'col': col, 'lig': lig, 'etat': 'en_attente'}\n",
    "\n",
    "def creer_etat(hopital, drones, survivants, zones_x=None):\n",
    "    \"\"\"Assemble un \u00e9tat de jeu minimal pour les tests.\"\"\"\n",
    "    return {\n",
    "        'tour': 1, 'score': 0,\n",
    "        'partie_finie': False, 'victoire': False,\n",
    "        'hopital': hopital,\n",
    "        'batiments': [],\n",
    "        'drones': drones,\n",
    "        'survivants': survivants,\n",
    "        'zones_x': zones_x or set(),\n",
    "        'historique': []\n",
    "    }\n",
    "\n",
    "print('Entit\u00e9s OK')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-regles",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. R\u00e8gles de jeu (rappel nb\_07)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "id": "cell-code-regles",
   "metadata": {},
   "execution_count": null,
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def calculer_cout(drone, cible, zones_x):\n",
    "    \"\"\"Co\u00fbt r\u00e9el du d\u00e9placement selon les r\u00e8gles officielles.\"\"\"\n",
    "    cout = COUT_TRANSPORT if drone['survivant'] else 1\n",
    "    if (cible[0], cible[1]) in zones_x:\n",
    "        cout += COUT_ZONE_X\n",
    "    return cout\n",
    "\n",
    "def peut_se_deplacer(drone, cible, zones_x):\n",
    "    \"\"\"Retourne (True, '') ou (False, raison).\"\"\"\n",
    "    if drone['hors_service']:\n",
    "        return False, f\"{drone['id']} est hors service\"\n",
    "    if drone['bloque'] > 0:\n",
    "        return False, f\"{drone['id']} est bloqu\u00e9\"\n",
    "    if not case_valide(cible[0], cible[1]):\n",
    "        return False, 'Hors de la grille'\n",
    "    if distance_chebyshev(drone['col'], drone['lig'], cible[0], cible[1]) > 1:\n",
    "        return False, 'Distance > 1'\n",
    "    cout = calculer_cout(drone, cible, zones_x)\n",
    "    if drone['batterie'] < cout:\n",
    "        return False, f\"Batterie insuffisante ({drone['batterie']} dispo, {cout} n\u00e9cessaire)\"\n",
    "    return True, ''\n",
    "\n",
    "def deplacer_drone(etat, did, cible):\n",
    "    \"\"\"D\u00e9place un drone et applique les effets (prise, livraison, recharge).\"\"\"\n",
    "    drone = etat['drones'][did]\n",
    "    ok, raison = peut_se_deplacer(drone, cible, etat['zones_x'])\n",
    "    if not ok:\n",
    "        ligne = f\"T{etat['tour']:02d}  {did}  REFUS: {raison}\"\n",
    "        etat['historique'].append(ligne)\n",
    "        return ligne\n",
    "    dep = (drone['col'], drone['lig'])\n",
    "    cout = calculer_cout(drone, cible, etat['zones_x'])\n",
    "    drone['batterie'] -= cout\n",
    "    drone['col'], drone['lig'] = cible\n",
    "    evenement = ''\n",
    "    if tuple(cible) == etat['hopital']:\n",
    "        if drone['survivant']:\n",
    "            etat['survivants'][drone['survivant']]['etat'] = 'sauve'\n",
    "            etat['score'] += 1\n",
    "            evenement = f\"LIVRAISON {drone['survivant']} +1pt\"\n",
    "            drone['survivant'] = None\n",
    "        drone['batterie'] = min(BATTERIE_MAX, drone['batterie'] + RECHARGE_HOPITAL)\n",
    "        evenement = evenement or f'RECHARGE +{RECHARGE_HOPITAL}'\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        for s in etat['survivants'].values():\n",
    "            if s['etat'] == 'en_attente' and s['col'] == cible[0] and s['lig'] == cible[1]:\n",
    "                drone['survivant'] = s['id']\n",
    "                s['etat'] = 'embarque'\n",
    "                evenement = f\"PRISE {s['id']}\"\n",
    "                break\n",
    "    if drone['batterie'] <= 0:\n",
    "        drone['hors_service'] = True\n",
    "        evenement = 'HS'\n",
    "    dep_s = pos_str(dep[0], dep[1])\n",
    "    arr_s = pos_str(cible[0], cible[1])\n",
    "    ligne = f\"T{etat['tour']:02d}  {did}  {dep_s}\u2192{arr_s}  bat:{drone['batterie']+cout}\u2192{drone['batterie']}  {evenement}\".rstrip()\n",
    "    etat['historique'].append(ligne)\n",
    "    return ligne\n",
    "\n",
    "print('R\u00e8gles OK')"
   ]
  },
  {
