    "## 5. Sc\u00e9nario de jeu complet\n",
    "\n",
    "Un sc\u00e9nario de 3 tours avec 1 drone, 1 survivant, 1 h\u00f4pital.\n",
    "\n",
    "- **Tour 1** : D1 se d\u00e9place vers S1 et le prend \u00e0 bord\n",
    "- **Tour 2** : D1 se d\u00e9place vers l'h\u00f4pital et livre S1\n",
    "- **Tour 3** : D1 reste sur l'h\u00f4pital (recharge)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "id": "cell-code-scenario",
   "metadata": {},
   "execution_count": null,
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Mise en place\n",
    "# H\u00f4pital en C3 = (col=2, lig=2)\n",
    "# D1 en A1 = (col=0, lig=0)\n",
    "# S1 en B2 = (col=1, lig=1)\n",
    "hopital = (2, 2)\n",
    "drones = {'D1': creer_drone('D1', 0, 0)}\n",
    "survivants = {'S1': creer_survivant('S1', 1, 1)}\n",
    "etat = creer_etat(hopital, drones, survivants)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"D\u00e9part : D1 en {pos_str(0,0)}, S1 en {pos_str(1,1)}, H\u00f4pital en {pos_str(2,2)}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
